{"tid":1229902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二三十年之後，今次反送中係新一代眼中會係點?","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:18:06.000Z","uid":230692,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e557fd2c549262f94295f4911e4498ea6754d4e","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:11:57.000Z","msg":"今次香港大和解，唔理你咩年齡咩身份，基本上所有界別都出黎反對，應該係香港97比人中共侵佔之後嘅第一次。但係過左今次之後，下一化又會點睇我地呢?<br />\n<br />\n小弟只希望今日嘅抗議，香港人可以勝利，令港共政府將惡法撤回。無人可以保證聽日會點，但係我只知道，我地做嘅野可以影響將來，甚至係下一代，比佢地一個好嘅環境生活。香港人嘅精神，永遠流傳！各位，6月16日，不撤回不罷休！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c958624dc4f996d0b902b2f55eb51298bdaec3","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a165ad7fb631713c5010b7b9f674a3e905d2efde","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09618816a178ea4e144ce868bdf6c81f4481d10f","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d456e1a9fbb54b730cd62eed283275bed1c7aa2","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c95456fdc8cc900695865042ccf74bfc4848e3c","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"推上去吖屌"},{"pid":"5a8b80ecc4ffebb2a5228d5b99f335b22b5fca57","tid":1229902,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"咁要視乎特區政府仲存唔存在"},{"pid":"a40aa7c60cdd02bc6e1efee06b154bef160c5d29","tid":1229902,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8b80ecc4ffebb2a5228d5b99f335b22b5fca57","tid":1229902,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"咁要視乎特區政府仲存唔存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-